; Coverage test for filters.cc
; Tests handle_value AMOUNT branch via collapse_posts::report_subtotal.
; When collapsing transactions with --collapse, the totals per account
; are passed through handle_value. For single-commodity amounts, the
; value type is AMOUNT, which hits post.amount = temp.as_amount

2024/01/15 Payee1
    Expenses:Food             $50.00
    Expenses:Drink            $10.00
    Assets:Cash              $-60.00

2024/01/15 Payee1
    Expenses:Gas              $40.00
    Assets:Cash              $-40.00

test reg Expenses --collapse
24-Jan-15 Payee1                <Total>                      $60.00       $60.00
24-Jan-15 Payee1                Expenses:Gas                 $40.00      $100.00
end test
